  "materials_text": "",
  "steps": [
    "Pipet 200 µl of the media you are growing the cell in (eg. SN media or Pro99 media) into wells A1 and A2 of a black 96-well microtiter plate. This is your blank.",
    "Pipet 200 µl of sample (the new culture you just inoculated) into wells B1 and B2 of the same plate. Ensure that there are no bubbles in the wells, as they will affect your readings. Pipet away any bubbles.",
    "Read the plate on the plate reader without the lid."
